hands_on_practices.solution:
我们需要计算作用于光滑标量场 $\phi$ 的两个协变导数的对易子。标量场的协变导数等于其偏导数：
$$

abla_{\mu}\phi=\partial_{\mu}\phi.
$$
因此，
$$

abla_{\mu}
abla_{
u}\phi=
abla_{\mu}(\partial_{
u}\phi).
$$
由于 $\partial_{
u}\phi$ 像协变矢量一样变换，其协变导数为
$$

abla_{\mu}(\partial_{
u}\phi)=\partial_{\mu}\partial_{
u}\phi-\Gamma^{\lambda}_{\mu
u}\,\partial_{\lambda}\phi.
$$
类似地，
$$

abla_{
u}
abla_{\mu}\phi=\partial_{
u}\partial_{\mu}\phi-\Gamma^{\lambda}_{
u\mu}\,\partial_{\lambda}\phi.
$$
对易子是
$$
[
abla_{\mu},
abla_{
u}]\phi=
abla_{\mu}
abla_{
u}\phi-
abla_{
u}
abla_{\mu}\phi
=(\partial_{\mu}\partial_{
u}\phi-\Gamma^{\lambda}_{\mu
u}\partial_{\lambda}\phi)-(\partial_{
u}\partial_{\mu}\phi-\Gamma^{\lambda}_{
u\mu}\partial_{\lambda}\phi).
$$
将各项分组可得
$$
[
abla_{\mu},
abla_{
u}]\phi=(\partial_{\mu}\partial_{
u}\phi-\partial_{
u}\partial_{\mu}\phi)-(\Gamma^{\lambda}_{\mu
u}-\Gamma^{\lambda}_{
u\mu})\partial_{\lambda}\phi.
$$
根据光滑标量场混合偏导数的相等性，
$$
\partial_{\mu}\partial_{
u}\phi=\partial_{
u}\partial_{\mu}\phi,
$$
以及克里斯托费尔符号在其下指标上的对称性，
$$
\Gamma^{\lambda}_{\mu
u}=\Gamma^{\lambda}_{
u\mu}.
$$
因此两项都为零，得到
$$
[
abla_{\mu},
abla_{
u}]\phi=0.
$$
